          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33911508/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33911508/" class="">第70页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/evoltnelis/" class=" " title="無聲">無聲</a>
                (百折不回孤行己意)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="33911508">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">元年大夫盟于宿，故来赴以名。例在七年。按：疑断句有误。《正义》体例多做“某例在某年”，此或当断作：元年，大夫盟于宿，故来。赴以名例在七年。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-01-05 15:41</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>元年大夫盟于宿，故来赴以名。例在七年。</q></blockquote>按：疑断句有误。《正义》体例多做“某例在某年”，此或当断作：<blockquote><q>元年，大夫盟于宿，故来。赴以名例在七年。</q></blockquote>
